* Memory profile

- go test -bench=. -benchmem -memprofile profile.out
- go tool pprof profile.out
- go tool pprof -web profile.out
- go tool pprof -http localhost:8080 profile.out



* CPU profile

- go test -bench=. -benchmem -cpuprofile profile.out
- go tool pprof profile.out
- go tool pprof -web profile.out
- go tool pprof -http localhost:8080 profile.out
